countries and territories around the world over  million rooms as of september   and additional  rooms in the development pipeline contents  history  founding and early years  marriott international  restructuring –  recent developments –present  operations  marriott brands  classic luxury  distinctive luxury  classic premium  distinctive premium  classic select  distinctive select  classic longer stays  distinctive longer stays  great america parks  see also  references  further reading  external links historyedit the key bridge marriott is the companys longest operating hotel founding and early yearsedit marriott was founded by john willard marriott in  when he and his wife alice sheets marriott opened a root beer stand in washington dc as a mormon missionary in the humid summers in washington dc marriott was convinced that what residents of the city needed was a place to get a cool drink the marriotts later expanded their enterprise into a chain of restaurants and hotels they opened their first hotel the twin bridges marriott motor hotel in arlington virginia in  their second hotel the key bridge marriott in the rosslyn neighborhood of the same city is marriott international’s longest continuously operating hotel and celebrated its th anniversary in  their son jw bill marriott jr led the company to spectacular worldwide growth during his more than year career in march  at age  he turned the ceo responsibilities over to arne sorenson while he assumed the title of executive chairman marriott internationaledit marriott international was formed in  when marriott corporation split into two companies marriott international and host marriott corporation in  marriott was the first hotel company worldwide to offer guests the option to book reservations online via the companys implementation of marsha marriotts automatic reservation system for hotel accommodations in april  marriott international acquired a  interest in ritzcarlton hotel company llc marriott international believed that it could increase sales and profit margins for the ritzcarlton a troubled chain with a significant number of properties either losing money or barely breaking even the cost to marriott was estimated to have been about  million in cash and assumed debt the next year marriott spent  million to take over the ritzcarlton atlanta and buy a majority interest in two properties owned by william johnson a real estate developer who had purchased the ritzcarlton boston in  and expanded his ritzcarlton holdings over the next twenty years the ritzcarlton began expansion into the lucrative timeshare market and undertook other new initiatives made financially possible by the deep pockets of marriott which also lent its own inhouse expertise in certain areas there were other benefits for ritzcarlton flowing from its relationship with marriott such as being able to take advantage of the parent companys reservation system and buying power the partnership was solidified in  when marriott acquired a majority ownership of the ritzcarlton today there are  ritzcarlton properties around the world restructuring –edit marriotts hotel in new york after the collapse of the world trade center towers on  the marriott world trade center was destroyed during the september   attacks in  marriott international began a major restructuring by spinning off many senior living services communities which is now part of sunrise senior living and marriott distribution services so that it could focus on hotel ownership and management the changes were completed in  marriott international owned ramada international hotels  resorts until its sale on september   to cendant in  marriott international and marriott vacation club international comprised two of the  entities that contributed the maximum of  to the second inauguration of president george w bush on july   marriott announced that all lodging buildings it operated in the united states and canada would become nonsmoking beginning september  the new policy includes all guest rooms restaurants lounges meeting rooms public space and employee work areas san diego marriott marquis  marina one of the highest revenuegenerating marriotts in the united states there were bombings at the islamabad marriott in  and at the jakarta marriott in  on november   marriott announced plans to add over  hotel properties by  the bulk of the additions will be in emerging markets india where it plans to have  hotel properties china and southeast asia on january   marriott said that pornography would not be included in the entertainment offered at new hotels which will use an internetbased video on demand system on december   jw marriott jr announced he would be stepping down as ceo of the company while assuming the role of executive chairman it was announced that arne sorenson would be taking over as ceo as of march  us republican presidential candidate mitt romney released his  federal income taxes on september   showing that he declared  in directors fees from marriott international despite the fact that news was released on january   that he had already stepped down from the marriott international board to run for president his had released  tax returns showed earnings in  of  in directors fees from marriott in february  bloomberg reported on romneys years overseeing tax matters for marriott which had included several scams quoting sen john mccain and legal actions brought against marriott which marriott lost in court over its manipulations of the us tax code in december  guinness world records recognized the fivestar jw marriott marquis hotel dubai as the worlds tallest hotel recent developments –presentedit the detroit marriott at the renaissance center is one of the tallest hotels in the western hemisphere on october   the us federal communications commission fcc fined marriott  for unlawful use of a containment feature of a wifi monitoring system to deliberately interfere with clientowned networks in the convention space of its gaylord opryland resort  convention center in nashville the scheme disrupted operation of clients mobile telephone hotspots by sending fraudulent wifi deauthentication packets marriott international inc the american hotel and lodging association and ryman hospitality properties responded by unsuccessfully petitioning the fcc to change the rules to allow them to continue the wilful jamming of clientowned networks a position which they were forced to abandon in early  in response to backlash from clients mainstream media major technology companies and national mobile carriers the incident drew unfavorable publicity to marriotts practice of charging transient lodgers –day for wifi connections routinely included in the base price at most discount chains and to exorbitant wifi fees typically – per device charged to conventiongoers at a time when the  billion annually in everincreasing incidental fees charged by usbased hotels to their lodgers was already drawing criticism and negative media coverage on january   marriott acquired canadian hotel chain delta hotels delta operates  hotels in canada on november   marriott announced the acquisition of starwood hotels and resorts worldwide for  billion a competing offer for starwood at  billion from a consortium led by chinas anbang insurance group was announced march   moving starwood to cease the deal with marriott and pursue the offer from anbang insurance group after marriott raised its bid to  billion on march  starwood terminated the anbang agreement and proceeded again with the merger with marriott following all necessary regulatory approvals in the united states and around the world over the course of  marriott closed the merger with starwood on september   creating the worlds largest hotel company with over  properties  million rooms and a new portfolio of  brands the starwood acquisition gives marriott a larger nonus presence approximately  of starwood’s revenues are from foreign markets the acquisition is the largest of its sort since  when blackstone acquired hilton for  billion there is a  million breakup fee if the transaction is not completed executives noted that total transaction and integration expenditures may exceed  million operationsedit marriott is the first hotel chain to serve food that is completely free of trans fats at all of its north american properties the hotel is noted for providing copies of the book of mormon in addition to the holy bible in its rooms marriott brandsedit the ritzcarlton at la live los angeles newly opened jw marriott at la live a fairfield inn  suites in lake buena vista fl jw marriott desert springs indoor boat parking foyer frenchmans cove usvi a marriott vacation club resort as of september   marriott operates  brands internationally classic luxuryedit jw marriott the ritzcarlton st regis distinctive luxuryedit bulgari hotels  resorts edition hotels the luxury collection w hotels classic premiumedit delta hotels marriott marriott vacation club mvc sheraton distinctive premiumedit autograph collection marriott marquis design hotels gaylord hotels le méridien renaissance hotels tribute portfolio westin classic selectedit courtyard by marriott fairfield inn by marriott four points by sheraton protea hotels by marriott springhill suites by marriott distinctive selectedit ac hotels aloft hotels moxy hotels classic longer staysedit marriott executive apartments residence inn by marriott towneplace suites by marriott distinctive longer staysedit element by westin great america parksedit marriott developed three theme parks of which two theme parks were opened they operated as marriotts great america from  until  the parks were located in gurnee illinois santa clara california and a proposed but neverbuilt location in the washington dc area and were themed celebrating american history the americanthemed areas under marriotts tenure of ownership included carousel plaza the first section beyond the main gates smalltownthemed hometown square the great midwest livestock exposition at county fair with a turn of the century ruralfair theme yankee harbor inspired by a thcentury new england port yukon territory resembling a canadianalaskan logging camp and the french quartermodeled orleans place at opening the parks had nearly identical layouts in  marriott disposed of its theme park division both parks were sold and today are associated with national theme park chains the gurnee location was sold to six flags theme parks where it operates today as six flags great america the santa clara location was sold to the city of santa clara who retained the underlying property and sold the park to kings entertainment company renamed paramount parks in  from  to  the santa clara location was known as paramounts great america in  paramount parks was acquired by cedar fair entertainment company the santa clara park operates today as californias great america in the years after their sale the layouts of the parks have diverged substantially see alsoedit list of chainedbrand hotels list of hotels maryland portal companies portal referencesedit   best companies to work for  – marriott international – fortune cnn   marriott fact book marriott international inc retrieved on march   p  i corporate profile corporate office marriott international inc  fernwood road bethesda md   jw marriott hotels  resorts  marriott news center newsmarriottcom retrieved    required fieldconfirmation number  about marriott hotels  marriott corporate business information marriottcom retrieved    marriott international inc md form k received   secfilingsnasdaqcom retrieved    remembrances of mom  marriott on the move blogsmarriottcom  retrieved    j willard marriott entrepreneurcom retrieved    root beer roots washingtonpostcom retrieved    key bridge marriott hotel prepares for th anniversary with  million renovation of event space  archive theopenpresscom  retrieved    magazine article forbescom retrieved    history of marriott internatio